181
00:16:38,580 --> 00:16:40,179
[SPEAKER_01] Što je važno?

182
00:16:40,179 --> 00:16:42,399
[SPEAKER_01] Kada ja otvorim svoje duhovne oči,

183
00:16:42,399 --> 00:16:43,340
[SPEAKER_01] kada molim Boga,

184
00:16:43,340 --> 00:16:45,159
