188
00:16:52,799 --> 00:16:56,580
[SPEAKER_01] Trebam početi raditi intenzivno na sebi.

189
00:16:56,580 --> 00:17:01,299
[SPEAKER_01] Zamislite još u jednoj etapi duhovnog rasta

190
00:17:01,299 --> 00:17:03,440
