202
00:17:42,319 --> 00:17:44,319
[SPEAKER_01] Davao im je novac.

203
00:17:44,319 --> 00:17:48,940
[SPEAKER_01] I zamislite, on dolazi u svoj grad gdje ga svi znaju.

204
00:17:48,940 --> 00:17:50,400
[SPEAKER_01] I znate što radi?

205
00:17:50,400 --> 00:17:55,559
