207
00:17:57,680 --> 00:18:00,059
[SPEAKER_01] Koliko je se ponizio, a zašto?

208
00:18:00,059 --> 00:18:03,160
[SPEAKER_01] E tu sada ima jedna zanimljiva stvar.

209
00:18:03,160 --> 00:18:10,700
[SPEAKER_01] Franjo je ciljano nije više htio dijeliti milostinju,

210
00:18:10,700 --> 00:18:12,279
