222
00:18:49,440 --> 00:18:52,299
[SPEAKER_01] ali vidite sveti Franjo ih nije krio.

223
00:18:52,299 --> 00:18:55,039
[SPEAKER_01] Išao je i raditi protiv njih.

224
00:18:55,359 --> 00:18:57,660
