1227
00:41:32,539 --> 00:41:33,920
[SPEAKER_00] pohađam Svjetu mislu.

1228
00:41:33,920 --> 00:41:35,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ali nisam samo na nedeljnih mislama.

1229
00:41:35,900 --> 00:41:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] A reci mi evo,

1230
00:41:37,500 --> 00:41:39,719
[SPEAKER_01] kada doživimo Boga,

1231
00:41:39,719 --> 00:41:41,500
[SPEAKER_01] kada imamo iskustvo živoga Boga,

1232
00:41:41,659 --> 00:41:43,619
[SPEAKER_01] onda to ne možemo čuvati samo za sebe.

1233
00:41:43,619 --> 00:41:45,320
[SPEAKER_01] Osobno te poznajem

1234
00:41:45,320 --> 00:41:47,420
[SPEAKER_01] i znam koliko si ljudi mladih

1235
00:41:47,420 --> 00:41:48,739
[SPEAKER_01] doveo tamo na Svjeti duh.

1236
00:41:48,739 --> 00:41:49,820
[SPEAKER_01] Ti si zapravo,

1237
00:41:49,820 --> 00:41:51,440
[SPEAKER_01] ja bih rekao poput Svjetog Franja,

1238
00:41:51,440 --> 00:41:52,860
[SPEAKER_01] dobio i svoje poslanje,

1239
00:41:52,860 --> 00:41:54,139
[SPEAKER_01] a to je da evangeliziraš.

1240
00:41:54,139 --> 00:41:56,099
[SPEAKER_01] Dosta si u tome dobar.

1241
00:41:56,099 --> 00:41:57,559
[SPEAKER_01] I što, evo,

1242
00:41:57,559 --> 00:41:59,179
[SPEAKER_01] možeš reći drugima,

1243
00:41:59,179 --> 00:42:02,679
[SPEAKER_01] jesi li doživio neku neugodnu situaciju

1244
00:42:02,679 --> 00:42:04,260
[SPEAKER_01] ili možda da nam ispričaš

1245
00:42:04,260 --> 00:42:05,199
[SPEAKER_01] neki lijepi događaje

1246
00:42:05,199 --> 00:42:06,039
[SPEAKER_01] kad si nekog frenda,

1247
00:42:06,039 --> 00:42:07,320
[SPEAKER_01] frendicu nekoga uspio

1248
00:42:07,320 --> 00:42:08,980
[SPEAKER_01] možda približiti crkvi.

1249
00:42:08,980 --> 00:42:10,139
[SPEAKER_01] Na koji si način to radio?

1250
00:42:10,960 --> 00:42:12,280
[SPEAKER_00] Nisam ništa nameću.

1251
00:42:12,280 --> 00:42:13,260
[SPEAKER_00] Čak sam,

1252
00:42:13,260 --> 00:42:14,880
[SPEAKER_00] da pač nisam ni pozivo,

1253
00:42:14,880 --> 00:42:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] nego sam prvo pričao

1254
00:42:16,159 --> 00:42:16,940
[SPEAKER_00] o svojim osjećajima,

1255
00:42:16,940 --> 00:42:18,059
[SPEAKER_00] šta se meni dogodilo.

1256
00:42:18,059 --> 00:42:19,960
[SPEAKER_00] I imam par osoba

1257
00:42:19,960 --> 00:42:21,760
[SPEAKER_00] koji nisu isto bili vezani

1258
00:42:21,760 --> 00:42:22,420
[SPEAKER_00] za crkvu,

1259
00:42:22,420 --> 00:42:23,840
[SPEAKER_00] nisu voljelić na misu,

1260
00:42:23,840 --> 00:42:25,559
[SPEAKER_00] nisu znali šta se događa tamo,

1261
00:42:25,559 --> 00:42:27,179
[SPEAKER_00] ali valjda kroz moju priču

1262
00:42:27,179 --> 00:42:27,679
[SPEAKER_00] i kad su videli

1263
00:42:27,679 --> 00:42:28,699
[SPEAKER_00] kako sam ja procjetao,

1264
00:42:28,699 --> 00:42:31,500
[SPEAKER_00] ljudi su se nesjesno odazvali.

1265
00:42:31,500 --> 00:42:33,659
[SPEAKER_00] Dovoljan je bio i jedan poziv

1266
00:42:33,659 --> 00:42:34,980
[SPEAKER_00] da bi onda poslije

1267
00:42:34,980 --> 00:42:38,420
[SPEAKER_00] i bez mog poziva dolazili,

1268
00:42:38,420 --> 00:42:39,619
[SPEAKER_01] nastavili s dolazicama.

1269
00:42:39,619 --> 00:42:41,000
[SPEAKER_01] To je ono što mladi,

1270
00:42:41,000 --> 00:42:42,860
[SPEAKER_01] pogotovo znam iz osobnog iskustva,

1271
00:42:42,860 --> 00:42:45,059
[SPEAKER_01] traže autentičnost.

1272
00:42:45,059 --> 00:42:47,480
[SPEAKER_01] Traže da je neko živi to iskustvo

1273
00:42:47,480 --> 00:42:48,699
[SPEAKER_01] i onda to pita ljudi sam.

1274
00:42:48,699 --> 00:42:49,539
[SPEAKER_01] Zašto si takav?

1275
00:42:49,539 --> 00:42:50,559
[SPEAKER_01] Otkud ti tolika snaga?

1276
00:42:50,559 --> 00:42:51,300
[SPEAKER_01] Otkud ti radost?

1277
00:42:51,300 --> 00:42:52,139
[SPEAKER_01] Otkud ti polet?

1278
00:42:52,139 --> 00:42:53,860
[SPEAKER_00] Da, i uz to onda ne treba

1279
00:42:53,860 --> 00:42:55,260
[SPEAKER_00] ni navaljivati nekom,

1280
00:42:55,260 --> 00:42:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] nametati mu.

1281
00:42:55,940 --> 00:42:56,500
[SPEAKER_00] Apsolutno.

1282
00:42:56,500 --> 00:42:57,219
[SPEAKER_00] Znam po sebi,

1283
00:42:57,219 --> 00:42:58,519
[SPEAKER_00] meni kad se nešto nametalo

1284
00:42:58,519 --> 00:43:00,300
[SPEAKER_00] jako teško mi je bilo to napraviti.

1285
00:43:00,300 --> 00:43:01,579
[SPEAKER_00] To je nije teško nego namoguće.

1286
00:43:01,579 --> 00:43:02,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ne bi to nikad napravili.

1287
00:43:02,519 --> 00:43:03,480
[SPEAKER_01] Zato ja uvijek kažem

1288
00:43:03,480 --> 00:43:05,000
[SPEAKER_01] da mi kršćani bi trebali biti

1289
00:43:05,000 --> 00:43:05,860
[SPEAKER_01] takvi kršćani,

1290
00:43:05,860 --> 00:43:06,760
[SPEAKER_01] takvi vjernici,

1291
00:43:06,760 --> 00:43:08,139
[SPEAKER_01] da ljudi nama prilaze

1292
00:43:08,139 --> 00:43:09,659
[SPEAKER_01] i pitaju pa zašto si takav.

1293
00:43:09,659 --> 00:43:10,980
[SPEAKER_01] Veselje, osmi.

1294
00:43:10,980 --> 00:43:11,679
[SPEAKER_01] Tako je.

1295
00:43:11,679 --> 00:43:13,059
[SPEAKER_01] Ne da se mi namećemo njima.

1296
00:43:13,059 --> 00:43:13,679
[SPEAKER_01] To je uvijek govorim

1297
00:43:13,679 --> 00:43:15,239
[SPEAKER_01] kad pričamo uličnoj evangelizaciji

1298
00:43:15,239 --> 00:43:15,699
[SPEAKER_01] i ostalom.

1299
00:43:15,699 --> 00:43:17,039
[SPEAKER_01] Ljudi, mi su smisektaši

1300
00:43:17,039 --> 00:43:19,280
[SPEAKER_01] koji onda vuku ljude za rukavi

1301
00:43:19,280 --> 00:43:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] i nameću svoje.

1302
00:43:20,079 --> 00:43:20,280
[SPEAKER_01] Ne.

1303
00:43:20,280 --> 00:43:22,380
[SPEAKER_01] Mi bi trebali biti samo takvi

1304
00:43:22,380 --> 00:43:23,760
[SPEAKER_01] da sami ljudi pitaju

1305
00:43:23,760 --> 00:43:24,659
[SPEAKER_01] zašto ste takvi

1306
00:43:24,659 --> 00:43:26,159
[SPEAKER_01] i gdje mi to možemo dobiti.

1307
00:43:26,159 --> 00:43:28,119
[SPEAKER_01] I to je ono samo po sebi

1308
00:43:28,119 --> 00:43:29,719
[SPEAKER_01] prepoznatljivo.

1309
00:43:29,719 --> 00:43:31,780
[SPEAKER_01] Tako da, svakako,

1310
00:43:31,780 --> 00:43:33,659
[SPEAKER_01] danas kada pričamo

1311
00:43:33,659 --> 00:43:35,800
[SPEAKER_01] o re-evangelizaciji crkve,

1312
00:43:35,800 --> 00:43:37,000
[SPEAKER_01] o promjenama,

1313
00:43:37,000 --> 00:43:38,539
[SPEAKER_01] ono što je evo i Sveti Franjo

1314
00:43:38,539 --> 00:43:39,780
[SPEAKER_01] stavio svoje rame

1315
00:43:39,780 --> 00:43:40,920
[SPEAKER_01] unutar crkve,

1316
00:43:40,920 --> 00:43:41,539
[SPEAKER_01] ne izvana,

1317
00:43:41,539 --> 00:43:42,659
[SPEAKER_01] meni je drago

1318
00:43:42,659 --> 00:43:43,800
[SPEAKER_01] da se više vas mladi

1319
00:43:43,800 --> 00:43:44,739
[SPEAKER_01] dolazi i moli,

1320
00:43:44,739 --> 00:43:45,900
[SPEAKER_01] da se više mladi

1321
00:43:45,900 --> 00:43:46,980
[SPEAKER_01] koji evangelizire,

1322
00:43:46,980 --> 00:43:48,139
[SPEAKER_01] koji svojim leđima

1323
00:43:48,139 --> 00:43:49,860
[SPEAKER_01] podupiru crkvu

1324
00:43:49,860 --> 00:43:51,739
[SPEAKER_01] i mislim da nema straha.

1325
00:43:51,860 --> 00:43:53,320
[SPEAKER_01] crkva će ostati,

1326
00:43:53,320 --> 00:43:54,679
[SPEAKER_01] jer je sve više vas

1327
00:43:54,679 --> 00:43:56,019
[SPEAKER_01] mladih koji se zapravo

1328
00:43:56,019 --> 00:43:57,360
[SPEAKER_01] na tom području

1329
00:43:57,360 --> 00:43:58,320
[SPEAKER_01] zaista dajete.

1330
00:43:58,320 --> 00:43:59,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ja isto vjerujem.

1331
00:43:59,360 --> 00:44:01,480
[SPEAKER_00] Jer dok ja nisam pohodio

1332
00:44:01,480 --> 00:44:03,219
[SPEAKER_00] crkvu i susrete neke,

1333
00:44:03,219 --> 00:44:04,179
[SPEAKER_00] mislio sam da nema

1334
00:44:04,179 --> 00:44:05,099
[SPEAKER_00] mladih uopće u crkvu.

1335
00:44:05,099 --> 00:44:06,320
[SPEAKER_00] To su samo stare bakice,

1336
00:44:06,320 --> 00:44:07,940
[SPEAKER_00] možda pokoj čovjek

1337
00:44:07,940 --> 00:44:09,559
[SPEAKER_00] i žena u srednjim godinama,

1338
00:44:09,559 --> 00:44:11,420
[SPEAKER_00] ali kad sam krenuo

1339
00:44:11,420 --> 00:44:13,239
[SPEAKER_00] i vidim da svakodnevno

1340
00:44:13,239 --> 00:44:14,159
[SPEAKER_00] sve više i više

1341
00:44:14,159 --> 00:44:15,679
[SPEAKER_00] mladih je u crkvu.

1342
00:44:15,679 --> 00:44:16,559
[SPEAKER_00] I vjerujem da će

1343
00:44:16,559 --> 00:44:17,719
[SPEAKER_00] u Hrvatskoj,

1344
00:44:17,719 --> 00:44:18,480
[SPEAKER_00] da će crkva

1345
00:44:18,480 --> 00:44:19,780
[SPEAKER_00] ići jako dobrim putem.

1346
00:44:19,780 --> 00:44:20,599
[SPEAKER_01] Istina je.

1347
00:44:21,099 --> 00:44:22,059
[SPEAKER_01] Kao mladi čovjek,

1348
00:44:22,059 --> 00:44:23,340
[SPEAKER_01] šta bi slobodno

1349
00:44:23,340 --> 00:44:24,440
[SPEAKER_01] reci jezla smo na radio,

1350
00:44:24,440 --> 00:44:25,139
[SPEAKER_01] da je javno,

1351
00:44:25,139 --> 00:44:27,460
[SPEAKER_01] šta bi rekao nama svećenicima?

1352
00:44:27,460 --> 00:44:28,639
[SPEAKER_01] Što bi poručio,

1353
00:44:28,639 --> 00:44:30,199
[SPEAKER_01] možda da li trebamo

1354
00:44:30,199 --> 00:44:31,219
[SPEAKER_01] promijeniti pristup

1355
00:44:31,219 --> 00:44:32,119
[SPEAKER_01] neki u crkvi,

1356
00:44:32,119 --> 00:44:33,780
[SPEAKER_01] da li imaš li možda

1357
00:44:33,780 --> 00:44:35,079
[SPEAKER_01] neki savjet, sugesti?

1358
00:44:35,079 --> 00:44:35,460
[SPEAKER_00] Pa dobro,

1359
00:44:35,460 --> 00:44:36,460
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam zadnje vrijeme

1360
00:44:36,460 --> 00:44:38,239
[SPEAKER_00] dosta u kontaktu

1361
00:44:38,239 --> 00:44:38,380
[SPEAKER_00] sa svećenicima.

1362
00:44:38,380 --> 00:44:39,940
[SPEAKER_00] to znam da si brutalno iskala.

1363
00:44:39,940 --> 00:44:41,320
[SPEAKER_00] I to isto.

1364
00:44:41,320 --> 00:44:42,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ali u zadnje vrijeme

1365
00:44:42,840 --> 00:44:44,260
[SPEAKER_00] sam dostao kontaktu

1366
00:44:44,260 --> 00:44:45,099
[SPEAKER_00] sa svećenicima

1367
00:44:45,099 --> 00:44:45,739
[SPEAKER_00] koji su u radu

1368
00:44:45,739 --> 00:44:46,559
[SPEAKER_00] s mladima.

1369
00:44:46,559 --> 00:44:47,500
[SPEAKER_00] I tu je

1370
00:44:47,500 --> 00:44:48,539
[SPEAKER_00] po meni za sad

1371
00:44:48,539 --> 00:44:49,019
[SPEAKER_00] sve u redu.

1372
00:44:49,019 --> 00:44:49,940
[SPEAKER_00] Više je problem

1373
00:44:49,940 --> 00:44:50,739
[SPEAKER_00] možda u nekim manjim

1374
00:44:50,739 --> 00:44:51,260
[SPEAKER_00] sredinama,

1375
00:44:51,260 --> 00:44:52,500
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je samo jedan svećenik,

1376
00:44:52,500 --> 00:44:52,940
[SPEAKER_00] gdje je neki

1377
00:44:52,940 --> 00:44:53,940
[SPEAKER_00] stari svećenik

1378
00:44:53,940 --> 00:44:56,519
[SPEAKER_00] koji ne pokušava

1379
00:44:56,519 --> 00:44:57,440
[SPEAKER_00] na neki drugi način

1380
00:44:57,440 --> 00:44:58,440
[SPEAKER_00] preći u mladima.

1381
00:44:58,440 --> 00:44:59,440
[SPEAKER_00] Nego samo tupi,

1382
00:44:59,440 --> 00:45:00,400
[SPEAKER_00] ne idete u crku,

1383
00:45:00,400 --> 00:45:01,480
[SPEAKER_00] morate doći u crku,

1384
00:45:01,480 --> 00:45:02,360
[SPEAKER_00] ne idete u crku,

1385
00:45:02,360 --> 00:45:03,840
[SPEAKER_00] ovakvi ste,

1386
00:45:03,840 --> 00:45:04,380
[SPEAKER_00] onakvi ste,

1387
00:45:04,380 --> 00:45:05,699
[SPEAKER_00] onda ti osjetiš

1388
00:45:05,699 --> 00:45:06,480
[SPEAKER_00] možda osudu

1389
00:45:06,480 --> 00:45:07,900
[SPEAKER_00] ako te nekoj ne osuđuje.

1390
00:45:07,900 --> 00:45:09,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ti kad si u grijehu,

1391
00:45:09,900 --> 00:45:10,199
[SPEAKER_00] loše,

1392
00:45:10,199 --> 00:45:10,820
[SPEAKER_00] kad živiš,

1393
00:45:10,820 --> 00:45:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] ti kroz...

1394
00:45:12,159 --> 00:45:13,599
[SPEAKER_00] I pohvalu možeš sebi

1395
00:45:13,599 --> 00:45:16,119
[SPEAKER_00] protumačiti kao osudu.

1396
00:45:16,119 --> 00:45:17,360
[SPEAKER_00] Jesi pročitao ovu knjigu?

1397
00:45:17,360 --> 00:45:17,679
[SPEAKER_00] Jesam.

1398
00:45:17,679 --> 00:45:18,420
[SPEAKER_00] I?

1399
00:45:18,420 --> 00:45:19,760
[SPEAKER_00] Reci slušateljima,

1400
00:45:19,760 --> 00:45:20,420
[SPEAKER_00] dobra ili nije?

1401
00:45:20,579 --> 00:45:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] I je.

1402
00:45:20,880 --> 00:45:23,980
[SPEAKER_00] I meni što je ostalo

1403
00:45:23,980 --> 00:45:25,019
[SPEAKER_00] jako iz te knjige,

1404
00:45:25,019 --> 00:45:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] ono što mi bijaše gorko

1405
00:45:26,539 --> 00:45:27,579
[SPEAKER_00] postade mi slatko,

1406
00:45:27,579 --> 00:45:28,960
[SPEAKER_00] a što mi bijaše slatko

1407
00:45:28,960 --> 00:45:30,019
[SPEAKER_00] postade mi gorko.

1408
00:45:30,019 --> 00:45:32,440
[SPEAKER_00] To mi se urezalo u pamćenju.

1409
00:45:32,440 --> 00:45:33,239
[SPEAKER_01] A vidim ja da ti

1410
00:45:33,239 --> 00:45:34,539
[SPEAKER_00] dobro poznaješ Franje

1411
00:45:34,539 --> 00:45:35,780
[SPEAKER_00] i Franjeva što to je lijepo.

1412
00:45:35,780 --> 00:45:37,579
[SPEAKER_00] Pa, ja sam ko mali

1413
00:45:37,579 --> 00:45:38,400
[SPEAKER_00] govorio da su za mene

1414
00:45:38,400 --> 00:45:39,500
[SPEAKER_00] samo fratri svećenici.

1415
00:45:39,500 --> 00:45:43,920
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mislim sad tako.

1416
00:45:43,920 --> 00:45:46,440
[SPEAKER_00] To je dobro.

1417
00:45:46,440 --> 00:45:47,460
[SPEAKER_01] Evo,

1418
00:45:47,460 --> 00:45:49,260
[SPEAKER_01] meni je drago da si

1419
00:45:49,260 --> 00:45:50,480
[SPEAKER_01] večeras ovdje sa nama,

1420
00:45:50,579 --> 00:45:52,599
[SPEAKER_01] mlade si već pozvao

1421
00:45:52,599 --> 00:45:53,139
[SPEAKER_01] u četvrtak

1422
00:45:53,139 --> 00:45:54,039
[SPEAKER_01] da nam se pridruže.

1423
00:45:54,039 --> 00:45:55,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ponoviću još jednom

1424
00:45:55,179 --> 00:45:56,260
[SPEAKER_01] za one koji ne znaju

1425
00:45:56,260 --> 00:45:58,199
[SPEAKER_01] da ovo je

1426
00:45:58,199 --> 00:45:58,739
[SPEAKER_01] na radiju

1427
00:45:58,739 --> 00:46:00,039
[SPEAKER_01] Duhovno-duhovite večeri,

1428
00:46:00,039 --> 00:46:01,079
[SPEAKER_01] nose isto ime

1429
00:46:01,079 --> 00:46:02,260
[SPEAKER_01] onim živim susjetima

1430
00:46:02,260 --> 00:46:03,159
[SPEAKER_01] koji su u crkvi.

1431
00:46:03,159 --> 00:46:04,559
[SPEAKER_01] Dragi vjenici,

1432
00:46:04,559 --> 00:46:05,800
[SPEAKER_01] mi smo svjesni

1433
00:46:05,800 --> 00:46:06,980
[SPEAKER_01] da se ne okupljamo

1434
00:46:06,980 --> 00:46:08,019
[SPEAKER_01] četvrtkom u crkvi

1435
00:46:08,019 --> 00:46:09,239
[SPEAKER_01] samo tamo,

1436
00:46:09,239 --> 00:46:10,860
[SPEAKER_01] mladi i zbog nas,

1437
00:46:10,860 --> 00:46:12,320
[SPEAKER_01] nego da često molimo

1438
00:46:12,320 --> 00:46:13,300
[SPEAKER_01] za sve vas

